1
00:00:11,160 --> 00:00:12,080
Come on, Baoyuan.

2
00:00:12,270 --> 00:00:13,080
Be careful.

3
00:00:14,080 --> 00:00:15,590
All right, just see us off here.

4
00:00:15,750 --> 00:00:16,920
Thanks, guys.

5
00:00:18,070 --> 00:00:19,000
All right, just see us off here.

6
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:20,030
You all shall go back now.

7
00:00:20,160 --> 00:00:21,030
Come on in.

8
00:00:22,320 --> 00:00:23,230
Thank you.

9
00:00:23,230 --> 00:00:23,920
Take care of Baoyuan.

10
00:00:23,920 --> 00:00:24,510
Thank you.

11
00:00:24,510 --> 00:00:25,120
Sure, I will.

12
00:00:25,710 --> 00:00:26,480
Zhuangzhuang.

13
00:00:27,760 --> 00:00:28,390
Zhuangzhuang.

14
00:00:30,190 --> 00:00:30,870
- It's Dad.
- Zhuangzhuang.

15
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:33,670
Come on, call your dad.

16
00:00:34,430 --> 00:00:35,150
Dad.

17
00:00:36,710 --> 00:00:37,640
Let me hug you, come on.

18
00:00:37,670 --> 00:00:38,750
Let me hug you.

19
00:00:41,070 --> 00:00:42,030
This kid...

20
00:00:43,960 --> 00:00:45,150
He'll get used to it.

21
00:00:45,470 --> 00:00:47,520
You haven't hugged him for eight years.

22
00:00:49,750 --> 00:00:51,240
Come on, sit down.

23
00:00:51,670 --> 00:00:52,710
I'll get your slippers.

24
00:00:58,960 --> 00:01:00,390
This cabinet is new.

25
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:02,390
So you can come back
with a new piece of furniture

26
00:01:02,750 --> 00:01:03,880
to get rid of the bad luck.

27
00:01:09,510 --> 00:01:10,790
Change into slippers.

28
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:12,230
They'll make you feel more comfortable.

29
00:01:12,950 --> 00:01:13,840
No need.

30
00:01:16,510 --> 00:01:17,280
Is it okay?

31
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:19,120
The couch is pretty comfy, isn't it?

32
00:01:58,790 --> 00:01:59,640
Baoyuan,

33
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:01,230
here, have some water.

34
00:02:03,870 --> 00:02:05,070
You've started reading?

35
00:02:08,430 --> 00:02:09,240
Yes.

36
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:12,280
To pass the time while you're away.

37
00:02:12,310 --> 00:02:13,630
And to occupy myself.

38
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:26,400
Zhuangzhuang's got a lot of awards.

39
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,630
He's an outstanding student.

40
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:30,120
He usually stays in this room.

41
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:31,520
Zhuangzhuang, stop playing.

42
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,520
Do your homework.

43
00:02:34,190 --> 00:02:35,240
Listen to your mom

44
00:02:35,590 --> 00:02:36,630
and study hard.

45
00:02:42,910 --> 00:02:44,080
This is our room.

46
00:02:53,710 --> 00:02:54,400
Let me help you.

47
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,030
Give it to me.

48
00:03:15,190 --> 00:03:16,360
You're still as beautiful as ever.

49
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,800
Your hair's gone gray.

50
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:29,960
Did you think

51
00:03:31,310 --> 00:03:33,080
I'd never get out?

52
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:40,280
What do you mean, Baoyuan?

53
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,190
Baoyuan!

54
00:03:46,590 --> 00:03:48,000
You've got a kept man,

55
00:03:48,430 --> 00:03:50,030
you tricked me into going to prison,

56
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:52,710
and you've taken over my property.

57
00:03:52,750 --> 00:03:53,630
I'll kill you.

58
00:04:09,150 --> 00:04:09,910
Mom.

59
00:04:13,910 --> 00:04:14,910
Have you finished your homework?

60
00:04:17,510 --> 00:04:18,430
Your mom is tired.

61
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,680
Let her sleep for a while.

62
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,750
Go and play, Zhuangzhuang.

63
00:05:55,450 --> 00:05:59,090
[Sandstorm]
[Episode 10]

64
00:06:12,270 --> 00:06:13,240
Stop pretending.

65
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:15,040
You can't hold it in for much longer.

66
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:24,360
You're still as much of a tease

67
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,310
as you were eight years ago.

68
00:06:30,630 --> 00:06:32,310
I'm not as gullible
as I was eight years ago.

69
00:06:36,390 --> 00:06:37,360
You're so bad.

70
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:39,070
Did you really want to kill me?

71
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,560
It's been eight years.

72
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,310
I couldn't bear to let you die

73
00:06:45,510 --> 00:06:46,310
at once.

74
00:06:58,310 --> 00:07:00,240
Sorry, Baoyuan.

75
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,830
Sorry, I was wrong.

76
00:07:04,390 --> 00:07:05,310
Baoyuan,

77
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,310
I was forced to.

78
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:09,430
I met Guan Qiao's sister

79
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:12,480
when I was doing square dancing.

80
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:13,510
She told me

81
00:07:13,510 --> 00:07:15,630
he was a writer
and wanted to interview me,

82
00:07:15,630 --> 00:07:17,270
so she tricked me
into going to his house

83
00:07:18,630 --> 00:07:19,830
and he

84
00:07:22,870 --> 00:07:24,040
raped me.

85
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,240
He made me lie

86
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:32,000
to put you in prison.

87
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:34,000
He said if I didn't cooperate with him,

88
00:07:34,510 --> 00:07:36,950
he'd tell everyone that I cuckolded you

89
00:07:37,270 --> 00:07:38,560
and that you'd beat me to death,

90
00:07:38,830 --> 00:07:40,190
that I'd be worse than dead.

91
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:42,870
I was pregnant at the time.

92
00:07:42,870 --> 00:07:44,190
I was so scared.

93
00:07:44,190 --> 00:07:45,510
I was scared.

94
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:49,270
Guan Qiao told me

95
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:52,360
about you and Cheng Chun, too.

96
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,070
I was so angry.

97
00:07:55,070 --> 00:07:56,600
I said yes to him

98
00:07:57,390 --> 00:07:58,750
in a fit of pique.

99
00:07:58,870 --> 00:07:59,680
I'm sorry.

100
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:01,870
I'm sorry.

101
00:08:06,310 --> 00:08:07,120
Anyway,

102
00:08:09,070 --> 00:08:10,680
how did Cheng Chun die?

103
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:13,240
You didn't kill her,

104
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:15,360
and I didn't kill her, right?

105
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:17,720
That night at the heating station,

106
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:18,510
there were only you,

107
00:08:19,310 --> 00:08:20,870
Liu Sancheng and Wang Liang.

108
00:08:22,430 --> 00:08:24,240
Liu Sancheng is dead now.

109
00:08:25,390 --> 00:08:26,390
But why would Wang Liang

110
00:08:27,070 --> 00:08:28,720
lie to you?

111
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:29,870
Do you know
what Cheng Chun's relationship

112
00:08:29,870 --> 00:08:30,680
with them is?

113
00:08:31,310 --> 00:08:32,120
Now

114
00:08:32,510 --> 00:08:33,550
that you're released,

115
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,600
let's get to the bottom of this.

116
00:08:36,270 --> 00:08:37,600
If you kill me,

117
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,320
no one can help you.

118
00:08:40,390 --> 00:08:41,600
We'll never know

119
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:43,480
who the real murderer is.

120
00:08:44,150 --> 00:08:46,080
They're all our enemies.

121
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:47,750
I hate them.

122
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:50,600
Besides,

123
00:08:51,870 --> 00:08:53,550
we still have Zhuangzhuang,

124
00:08:53,670 --> 00:08:54,320
right?

125
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:59,550
Zhuangzhuang hasn't had a father
for eight years.

126
00:08:59,550 --> 00:09:01,480
If he loses hiss mum again,

127
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:03,200
he'll be pitiful.

128
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:04,670
We're both still young.

129
00:09:06,550 --> 00:09:08,440
The good times have just begun.

130
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:10,550
I am thinking

131
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:14,240
of giving you another child.

132
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:15,750
We

133
00:09:18,910 --> 00:09:21,150
are like two pieces of ginger
that can't be separated.

134
00:09:23,750 --> 00:09:25,030
You can't leave me,

135
00:09:26,150 --> 00:09:27,390
and I can't leave you.

136
00:09:30,270 --> 00:09:31,120
Baoyuan,

137
00:09:33,390 --> 00:09:34,120
in the future,

138
00:09:37,910 --> 00:09:39,600
you're going to need me

139
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:41,550
for a lot of things.

140
00:09:50,510 --> 00:09:51,600
You've got money for the bath,

141
00:09:51,630 --> 00:09:52,480
but not for me, right?

142
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:53,320
Lei.

143
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:54,120
Lei.

144
00:09:55,670 --> 00:09:56,360
I heard

145
00:09:56,750 --> 00:09:57,840
you got dumped by Sun Caiyun.

146
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,030
No.

147
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:01,600
No. Don't search me, Lei.

148
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:02,320
Give me two days.

149
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:03,440
Give me two days and I'll pay you.

150
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:04,630
Two days?

151
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:06,600
Think of something now.

152
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:09,080
When are you going to pay me?

153
00:10:10,510 --> 00:10:11,600
In these few days.

154
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:12,630
Lei.

155
00:10:13,270 --> 00:10:14,150
Caiyun.

156
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:14,910
What's going on?

157
00:10:14,910 --> 00:10:15,550
Caiyun.

158
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:18,320
No big deal. He owes me some money.

159
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,120
She didn't dump you?

160
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:20,790
We have a good relationship.

161
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:24,150
How much does he owe?

162
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:25,910
It's not much. 2,200 yuan.

163
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:27,150
Isn't it 2,000 yuan?

164
00:10:27,150 --> 00:10:28,240
What about interest?

165
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:30,150
Don't be so insensible.

166
00:10:30,510 --> 00:10:32,550
If Lei says 2,200 yuan, so be it.

167
00:10:33,030 --> 00:10:35,270
Don't bargain. Do you think
you're buying groceries?

168
00:10:35,550 --> 00:10:36,390
Let me see.

169
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:43,600
I'll pay you back 1,000 yuan first.

170
00:10:43,870 --> 00:10:45,390
- I'll send you the rest later.
- Okay.

171
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:47,510
I can trust you.

172
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:48,510
What are you doing?

173
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:50,790
Lei's just shaking my hand.

174
00:10:51,670 --> 00:10:52,200
Thank you.

175
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:53,390
All right,
let's drink together some day.

176
00:10:53,390 --> 00:10:54,120
Sure.

177
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:55,510
Goodbye, Lei.

178
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:58,960
What kind of project

179
00:10:59,030 --> 00:11:00,080
that costs so much money?

180
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:02,440
I lost in mahjong.

181
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:04,270
It's not about the bath.

182
00:11:05,390 --> 00:11:06,120
Is that so?

183
00:11:06,630 --> 00:11:07,870
We haven't seen each other
for a long time.

184
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:09,910
What have you been up to?

185
00:11:09,910 --> 00:11:10,720
Stop it.

186
00:11:11,320 --> 00:11:13,550
There are a lot of people coming
and going here.

187
00:11:14,750 --> 00:11:17,720
Ding Baoyuan is back.
He doesn't suspect us, does he?

188
00:11:18,670 --> 00:11:20,600
No, why would he?

189
00:11:21,150 --> 00:11:22,550
He's been in prison for eight years

190
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,670
and he's confused now.

191
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:26,910
Qiao, let's go.

192
00:11:26,910 --> 00:11:27,870
Come home with me.

193
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:29,390
Why would I go to your house?

194
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,360
Let him settle the score with me?

195
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:33,960
What score?

196
00:11:35,910 --> 00:11:37,360
You told me last time

197
00:11:37,670 --> 00:11:39,390
he could apply
for more than 2 million yuan

198
00:11:39,790 --> 00:11:41,150
in state compensation.

199
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:44,120
You're really smart.
He can really get that much money.

200
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:46,960
What did I say?

201
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:49,440
That's more than 2 million yuan.

202
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:51,510
What does he need all that money for?

203
00:11:52,150 --> 00:11:53,390
That's right.

204
00:11:53,750 --> 00:11:54,550
So

205
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:57,150
we need to find a way

206
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:58,720
to get our hands on the money.

207
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:00,960
I told him

208
00:12:01,270 --> 00:12:02,600
you're a lawyer

209
00:12:02,750 --> 00:12:04,750
and you can help him apply
for state compensation.

210
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:06,480
He believed it.

211
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:09,120
I don't know anything about the law.

212
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:10,200
I can't do it.

213
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,000
I... I'm not going.

214
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:11,670
Don't be a wimp.

215
00:12:12,660 --> 00:12:14,060
Be confident, will you?

216
00:12:14,150 --> 00:12:15,870
You've read so many books for nothing.

217
00:12:16,910 --> 00:12:18,870
Even if you don't think about yourself,

218
00:12:19,550 --> 00:12:21,550
you have to think
about me and Zhuangzhuang.

219
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:23,550
Once we've got the money,

220
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:26,550
Zhuangzhuang and I will leave

221
00:12:26,790 --> 00:12:28,150
this hellhole with you.

222
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:31,080
You're not really going
to give Zhuangzhuang and me

223
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:32,390
to Ding Baoyuan, are you?

224
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:34,240
Will it work?

225
00:12:36,030 --> 00:12:37,200
Why not?

226
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:39,550
You're so talented

227
00:12:39,910 --> 00:12:41,240
and you love to learn.

228
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:42,360
Get yourself

229
00:12:42,390 --> 00:12:44,960
some law books

230
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:46,440
and read and memorize them.

231
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:47,440
It will definitely work.

232
00:12:47,510 --> 00:12:48,440
I believe you.

233
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:51,270
I'll wait for you.

234
00:12:57,510 --> 00:12:58,150
Caiyun.

235
00:12:59,000 --> 00:12:59,670
Caiyun.

236
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:00,840
I'll wait for you.

237
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:03,150
Study hard.

238
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:14,550
Is he home?

239
00:13:14,550 --> 00:13:15,270
Yes.

240
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:16,080
Do I really have to do this?

241
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:17,150
Yes, come in.

242
00:13:17,510 --> 00:13:19,240
He's been locked up for eight years
and he's gone dumb.

243
00:13:19,750 --> 00:13:20,630
Will it work?

244
00:13:21,270 --> 00:13:22,270
Be confident.

245
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:25,360
Baoyuan,

246
00:13:25,550 --> 00:13:26,510
The lawyer, Mr. Guan, is here.

247
00:13:30,550 --> 00:13:31,360
Hello.

248
00:13:32,240 --> 00:13:33,270
Let me introduce you to each other.

249
00:13:33,440 --> 00:13:34,750
This is Guan Qiao.

250
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:36,600
He used to be a famous writer,

251
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:37,670
now he's a lawyer.

252
00:13:37,910 --> 00:13:40,080
He's both a writer and a lawyer.

253
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:41,270
Mr. Guan,

254
00:13:41,390 --> 00:13:43,720
we're counting on you
for Baoyuan's application

255
00:13:43,720 --> 00:13:44,750
for state compensation.

256
00:13:44,750 --> 00:13:45,480
No problem.

257
00:13:46,030 --> 00:13:46,750
Let's sit down and talk about it.

258
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:48,270
Have a seat.

259
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:49,840
Be careful.

260
00:13:50,150 --> 00:13:51,150
Mr. Guan,

261
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:53,000
I'm counting on you

262
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:54,870
for this trifle.

263
00:13:55,270 --> 00:13:56,870
No problem.

264
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:58,200
Here,

265
00:13:59,200 --> 00:13:59,960
have some water.

266
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:01,120
Sit properly.

267
00:14:04,440 --> 00:14:05,270
Mr. Guan,

268
00:14:05,390 --> 00:14:06,790
my husband said

269
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:09,200
to entrust this matter to you.

270
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:11,320
When it's done, you'll get your share.

271
00:14:11,750 --> 00:14:13,480
How much should we give him?

272
00:14:14,390 --> 00:14:15,150
It's up to you.

273
00:14:15,150 --> 00:14:16,150
It's up to me?

274
00:14:17,510 --> 00:14:18,150
Well...

275
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:20,150
What are the rules

276
00:14:20,150 --> 00:14:21,480
in your industry?

277
00:14:22,550 --> 00:14:26,440
What's the usual rate for the industry?

278
00:14:31,360 --> 00:14:33,440
We go by the compensation offer,

279
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:35,720
usually 20%, something like that.

280
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:36,750
Okay.

281
00:14:37,390 --> 00:14:39,510
Money doesn't matter to me.

282
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:41,200
I spent eight years in prison

283
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:43,080
and learned this one thing.

284
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:43,720
Yes.

285
00:14:43,750 --> 00:14:45,390
So, Mr. Guan,

286
00:14:45,750 --> 00:14:47,080
Please go

287
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:48,630
with Ding.

288
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:49,670
Where to?

